    Description:	Ubuntu 18.04.3 LTS
    Release:	18.04
    Codename:	bionic

    Alternative:
    devnet@devnet:/$ cat /etc/os-release 
        NAME="Ubuntu"
        VERSION="18.04.3 LTS (Bionic Beaver)"
